Management of acute kidney injury in symptomatic multiple myeloma.

Bridoux F(1), Leung N(2), Belmouaz M(3), Royal V(4), Ronco P(5), Nasr SH(6), 
Fermand JP(7); International Kidney and Monoclonal Gammopathy Research Group.

Author information:
(1)Department of Nephrology, Dialysis, and Renal Transplantation, CIC INSERM 
