546. Int J Equity Health. 2021 Jan 14;20(1):36. doi: 10.1186/s12939-020-01356-4.

A qualitative study of barriers to employment experienced by people living with 
HIV in Toronto and Ottawa.

Perri M(1)(2), Craig-Neil A(1), Gaspar M(2), Hunter C(3)(4), Kendall 
C(5)(6)(7)(8)(9), Alexander O(1), Pinto AD(10)(11)(12)(13).

Author information:
(1)Upstream Lab, MAP/Centre for Urban Health Solutions, Li Ka Shing Knowledge 
Institute, Unity Health Toronto, 30 Bond St, Toronto, Ontario, M5B 1W8, Canada.
(2)Dalla Lana School of Public Health, University of Toronto, 155 College St, 
